org.odk.collect.android.injection.config

Interface AppDependencyComponent


  • @Singleton
 @Component(modules=AppDependencyModule.class)
public interface AppDependencyComponent
    Dagger component for the application. Should include application level Dagger Modules and be built with Application object. Add an `inject(MyClass myClass)` method here for objects you want to inject into so Dagger knows to wire it up. Annotated with @Singleton so modules can include @Singletons that will be retained at an application level (as this an instance of this components is owned by the Application object). If you need to call a provider directly from the component (in a test for example) you can add a method with the type you are looking to fetch (`MyType myType()`) to this interface. To read more about Dagger visit: https://google.github.io/dagger/users-guide
